44
00:03:15,050 --> 00:03:17,050
Old Rhino and everyone
in the Hall of Defense

45
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:19,050
are all strong and fierce

46
00:03:19,050 --> 00:03:21,050
that they blocked the front like a wall.

47
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:22,180
Chief Tang.

48
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,910
Thank you for your help

49
